data.description: Welcome to 6306 Loquat Grove Court, a beautiful new home on culdesac in Katy, TX. This 3 bed/3 bath property boasts 2,188 sq.ft of living space & a 6,721 sq.ft corner lot. As you enter the home, you'll immediately be struck by the open floor plan & vaulted ceilings, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The upgraded limestone featured in the kitchen adds an elegant touch, making it the perfect space for cooking & entertaining. The primary bedroom is located downstairs, along with an additional bedroom and bathroom, providing plenty of space for guests or a home office. Step outside to enjoy the extra-large covered patio & expansive yard, perfect for summer barbecues and outdoor activities. Upstairs, the home offers a spacious gameroom, additional bedroom with a full bathroom, & a walkout attic for extra storage. Room to make additional nook. 6306 Loquat Grove Court offers the perfect combination of style, comfort, & functionality, making it the ideal place to call home in Katy, Texas.
